Package: govhrcast
Title: Government Wage Bill Forecasting and Simulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simulation system for public sector workforce analytics.
    Allows World Bank country teams to simulate workforce policies, estimate
    wage bills under baseline or policy scenarios, and model retirement, hiring,
    promotion, and transfer dynamics using harmonized HRMIS data.
